# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The Wedding Sridha — what NOT to commit / deploy
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Admin editor (KEEP LOCAL, never deploy publicly) ────────────────
# These files let anyone edit the site. They must stay on your machine
# only. Edit locally → Export data.js → commit only data.js to publish.
admin.html
css/admin.css
js/admin.js

# ── OS / editor cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.log
*.swp
.vscode/
.idea/

# ── Local exports / backups (downloaded data.js you haven't deployed) ─
data-backup-*.js
*.bak

# ── Local server artefacts ──────────────────────────────────────────
.cache/
node_modules/
